        <mxCell id="useA_note" parent="1" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;fillColor=#ECE9F3;strokeColor=#7A6B98;fontSize=13;fontColor=#3D4A5C;align=left;spacingLeft=14;spacingTop=10" value="What it&#39;s for&#xa;&#xa;When a student is building a mind map and types&#xa;&quot;ER Model&quot;, the AI can suggest related ideas it&#xa;already knows from the course — Primary Key,&#xa;Normalisation, EER Model — and explain how&#xa;they connect.&#xa;&#xa;The mind-map shape (not just plain text) lets&#xa;the AI recommend the right next idea, not&#xa;random ones." vertex="1">
